#

Truffle Risotto

40 min
$12
450 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Main CourseVegetarian

Tags:

ItalianComfort FoodMain Course

Description

A creamy and rich risotto infused with the luxurious flavor of truffle oil, perfect for a comforting meal.

Ingredients

  • arborio rice: 1 cup
  • chicken or vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • onion, finely chopped: 1 small
  • garlic, minced: 2 cloves
  • white wine: 1/2 cup
  • parmesan cheese, grated: 1/2 cup
  • truffle oil: 2 tablespoons
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • fresh parsley, chopped: for garnish
